text.tspan: Welcome to SET! In this game it is your goal
to find sets before your time runs out.
There are 12 cards available at all times.
Each card has 4 properties: color, amount, shading and symbol.
To find a set you have to select 3 cards.
A set is valid if for all 4 properties,
either all three cards are the same or all three cards are different.
During the game, a timer is visible on the screen.
Your goal is to find a set before the time runs out.
If you succeed, you gain a point.

Do not worry though, cards will
